          "reviewBody": "Went to school here in 1984 / 85.  I have to say it was a mix of experiences having come from Canada, but I still hold on to the memories often.  I’m a little sad to see all the changes over the years and hope to see Mussoorie again soon to relive those memories.  In retrospect, I owe a lot to my short time attending Mussoorie.",
