            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I'm an ex student of the school. I found most of my talent and my passion in the hallways and library of Mussoorie Public School. Its a great and a spiritual emvironment here. Great teachers back when I was there in the school (2000 - 2011). A great place to be in. Great memories. I have spent 11 years of my life here and I must tell this to everyone that it was worth it. This great institution taught me values of life and how to achieve your goals. I'm greatly indebted to this great school and to my teachers. God Bless everyone!!",
